Class JsonSerializationAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wikidata.wdtk.client.DumpProcessingOutputAction
      • org.wikidata.wdtk.client.JsonSerializationAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DumpProcessingAction, EntityDocumentDumpProcessor, EntityDocumentProcessor

    public class JsonSerializationAction
extends DumpProcessingOutputAction
    This class represents an action of generating a JSON dump from data. It has no specific options.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch

      • isReady

        public boolean isReady()
        Description copied from interface: DumpProcessingAction
        Returns true if the action is ready to process a dump. An action that is insufficiently or wrongly configured can return false here to avoid being run.

        If this method is called on an action that is not ready, the action should print helpful information on the missing configuration to stdout as a side effect.

        Returns:
        true if ready to run
